tton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 02, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lcv1665702746747.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lcv1665702746747.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lcv1665702746747.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lcv1665702746747\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Normally, the Uniface installer automatically configures the Sentinel license\n      environment on Linux. However, if you ran the installer without root privileges, or you choose\n      the manual configuration option for some other reason, you must manually configure license\n      management.</p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__context_w4766ab1b5b1_w4767ab1b5_w4768ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__p_d65927e1_d65928e1_d65929e1\">To manually configure licenses, you need to run the\n            Uniface license utility (<span class=\"ph filepath\">ulic</span>) as root. For more information, see\n               <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qgt1690346679212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qgt1690346679212.html\" title=\"The Uniface License Management utility (ulic) is responsible for activating and downloading required Sentinel licenses, for checking out licenses, and renewing the lease on licenses on a regular basis. The licenses themselves are maintained by the Sentinel Cloud Server.\">Uniface License Management Utility (ulic)</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__li_d28766e1_d28767e1_d28768e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Run <span class=\"ph filepath\">ulic</span> as root:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /prep</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__li_d28769e1_d28770e1_d28771e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__p_d65930e1_d65931e1_d65932e1\">To activate a cloud-served license, run\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ulic</span>:</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"lines\">ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /act EntitlementID<br/>               </p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /act 77329e95-d153-4a4b-aa27-a62fadce </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__li_d28772e1_d28773e1_d28774e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__p_d65933e1_d65934e1_d65935e1\">To activate multiple cloud-served licenses, run\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ulic</span> with each Entitlement ID as a separate argument: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"lines\">ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /act EntitlementID /act EntitlementID<br/>               </p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /act 77329e95-d153-4a4b-aa27-a62fadce /act 85972e95-d143-5a5b-aa27-a39fadce</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__li_d28775e1_d28776e1_d28777e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"lcv1665702746747__p_d65936e1_d65937e1_d65938e1\">To specify an RMS server or license file, set\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LICENSE_OPTIONS</span> in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.asn</span> file:  </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[SETTINGS]\n$LICENSE_OPTIONS LM_LICENSE_FILE=\"a_dir/lservrc\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xna1665702718729.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xna1665702718729.html\" title=\"Set one or more license management options, according to your Sentinel license type.\">$LICENSE_OPTIONS</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Manually Configure Sentinel Licenses on Linux Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 02, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Normally, the Uniface installer automatically configures the Sentinel license environment on Linux. However, if you ran the installer without root privileges, or you choose the manual configuration option for some other reason, you must manually configure license management. To manually configure licenses, you need to run the Uniface license utility ( ulic ) as root. For more information, see Uniface License Management Utility (ulic) . Run ulic as root: ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /prep Copy To activate a cloud-served license, run ulic : ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /act EntitlementID For example: ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /act 77329e95-d153-4a4b-aa27-a62fadce Copy To activate multiple cloud-served licenses, run ulic with each Entitlement ID as a separate argument: ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /act EntitlementID /act EntitlementID For example: ulic /adm=USYSUNIFACE/adm /act 77329e95-d153-4a4b-aa27-a62fadce /act 85972e95-d143-5a5b-aa27-a39fadce Copy To specify an RMS server or license file, set $LICENSE_OPTIONS in the usys.asn file: [SETTINGS] $LICENSE_OPTIONS LM_LICENSE_FILE=\"a_dir/lservrc\" Copy For more information, see $LICENSE_OPTIONS . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}